events.text:
The marshlands is a teeming ecosystem full of marvelous wonder at times creating its own life.
This life has been becoming hostile rather recently for reasons I'm not sure of.
Go to the fungal forest west of here to investigate anything strange that might be the cause of their hostility.
Did you find anything strange in the forest?
Just as I feared, the corruption already spreaded and driven the spores mad. Hmmm... come back to me at a later time.
